<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Gatsby Starter Blog RSS Feed]]></title><description><![CDATA[A starter blog demonstrating what Gatsby can do.]]></description><link>https://sirius506775.github.io</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Sat, 07 Jan 2023 05:03:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[VScode 사용 중 스크립트 실행 불가에러 PSSecurityException 보안 오류 해결 방법]]></title><description><![CDATA[이 포스팅은 보안 오류: (") []. PSSecurityException 오류 해결 방법을 제공한다. 문제증상 VScode에서 npm으로 Gatsby…]]></description><link>https://sirius506775.github.io/error message/2023-vscode-1/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://sirius506775.github.io/error message/2023-vscode-1/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 06 Jan 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;이 포스팅은 보안 오류: (&quot;) []. PSSecurityException 오류 해결 방법을 제공한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;문제증상&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VScode에서 npm으로 Gatsby 설치 후 버젼을 확인하려고 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;gatsby -v&lt;/code&gt; 를 실행하니 아래와 같이 스크립트 실행 불가 에러가 발생하였다.
&lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; &quot;&gt;
      &lt;a class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot; href=&quot;/static/7fd5a9ea788778501149eb870a0d9159/31198/2023-error-1.png&quot; style=&quot;display: block&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 22.151898734177216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot; alt=&quot;result query&quot; title=&quot;result query&quot; src=&quot;/static/7fd5a9ea788778501149eb870a0d9159/f058b/2023-error-1.png&quot; srcset=&quot;/static/7fd5a9ea788778501149eb870a0d9159/c26ae/2023-error-1.png 158w,
/static/7fd5a9ea788778501149eb870a0d9159/6bdcf/2023-error-1.png 315w,
/static/7fd5a9ea788778501149eb870a0d9159/f058b/2023-error-1.png 630w,
/static/7fd5a9ea788778501149eb870a0d9159/31198/2023-error-1.png 694w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;해결과정&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;로그에서 말하는 PSSecurityException에 대해 검색해보니 보안 실행 정책 제한되어있기에 발생하는 오류인 것을 확인했다. 즉, 스크립트 실행 권한이 없다는 뜻이다.
스크립트를 실행할 수 있게 허용하려면 PowerShell 실행 정책을 Restricted에서 RemoteSigned 또는 Unrestricted로 설정해야한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PowerShell을 관리자 모드로 실행한다.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Windows Vista 이상 버전의 Windows에서 로컬 컴퓨터 LocalMachine 범위에 대 한 실행 정책을 변경 하는 명령을 실행 하려면 관리자 권한으로 실행해야한다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; &quot;&gt;
      &lt;a class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot; href=&quot;/static/6fcec11a8b8767c7fc60dfbfe6876dfb/ef3e1/2023-error-2.png&quot; style=&quot;display: block&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 44.93670886075949%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot; alt=&quot;result query&quot; title=&quot;result query&quot; src=&quot;/static/6fcec11a8b8767c7fc60dfbfe6876dfb/f058b/2023-error-2.png&quot; srcset=&quot;/static/6fcec11a8b8767c7fc60dfbfe6876dfb/c26ae/2023-error-2.png 158w,
/static/6fcec11a8b8767c7fc60dfbfe6876dfb/6bdcf/2023-error-2.png 315w,
/static/6fcec11a8b8767c7fc60dfbfe6876dfb/f058b/2023-error-2.png 630w,
/static/6fcec11a8b8767c7fc60dfbfe6876dfb/ef3e1/2023-error-2.png 759w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ol start=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;콘솔 창에 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Get-ExecutionPolicy -List&lt;/code&gt;를 입력하면 현재 세션에 영향을 주는 모든 실행 정책을 가져와서 우선 순위로 표시한다. 출력 결과를 보니 현재 실행 정책이 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Restricted&lt;/code&gt;로 제한되어 있음을 알 수 있다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 239px; &quot;&gt;
      &lt;a class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot; href=&quot;/static/26f8c648040a7de9a7d62a914d1eb701/4a279/2023-error-3.png&quot; style=&quot;display: block&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 52.53164556962025%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot; alt=&quot;result query&quot; title=&quot;result query&quot; src=&quot;/static/26f8c648040a7de9a7d62a914d1eb701/4a279/2023-error-3.png&quot; srcset=&quot;/static/26f8c648040a7de9a7d62a914d1eb701/c26ae/2023-error-3.png 158w,
/static/26f8c648040a7de9a7d62a914d1eb701/4a279/2023-error-3.png 239w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 239px) 100vw, 239px&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ol start=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;스크립트를 실행할 수 있게 허용하려면 실행 정책을 Restricted에서 RemoteSigned 또는 Unrestricted로 설정해야 한다. &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned&lt;/code&gt;을 입력해서 현재 실행 정책을 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;RemoteSigned&lt;/code&gt;로 변경하자.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; &quot;&gt;
      &lt;a class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot; href=&quot;/static/463d264ab375d54abcfdd3d0df1f63f3/34e70/2023-error-4.png&quot; style=&quot;display: block&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 24.050632911392405%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot; alt=&quot;result query&quot; title=&quot;result query&quot; src=&quot;/static/463d264ab375d54abcfdd3d0df1f63f3/f058b/2023-error-4.png&quot; srcset=&quot;/static/463d264ab375d54abcfdd3d0df1f63f3/c26ae/2023-error-4.png 158w,
/static/463d264ab375d54abcfdd3d0df1f63f3/6bdcf/2023-error-4.png 315w,
/static/463d264ab375d54abcfdd3d0df1f63f3/f058b/2023-error-4.png 630w,
/static/463d264ab375d54abcfdd3d0df1f63f3/40601/2023-error-4.png 945w,
/static/463d264ab375d54abcfdd3d0df1f63f3/34e70/2023-error-4.png 1053w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ol start=&quot;4&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;변경 상태를 확인하기 위해 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;GET-ExecutionPolicy&lt;/code&gt; 명령으로 현재 보안 실행 정책을 확인해보면 정상적으로 변경되어 있는 것을 확인할 수 있다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 346px; &quot;&gt;
      &lt;a class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot; href=&quot;/static/7ac8b0589753bb290bf680e2bd5668f6/8f77f/2023-error-5.png&quot; style=&quot;display: block&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 10.759493670886075%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAdElEQVQI1z2MUQrDIBQEcwH1hSANxFZaKxpbDd7/cFNioB/L7M7HTvu+Y63lOA5qrbTW6L2P7r0npUQphXVd+RRPfDtyeoyEsI1dv0/u7kZ4bUznQQgB5xw5Z2KMKKWY5xkRGTxzOYPWF5dFEDGIaIzRf/8Dg2s1b1TEjCQAAAAASUVORK5CYII=&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot; alt=&quot;result query&quot; title=&quot;result query&quot; src=&quot;/static/7ac8b0589753bb290bf680e2bd5668f6/8f77f/2023-error-5.png&quot; srcset=&quot;/static/7ac8b0589753bb290bf680e2bd5668f6/c26ae/2023-error-5.png 158w,
/static/7ac8b0589753bb290bf680e2bd5668f6/6bdcf/2023-error-5.png 315w,
/static/7ac8b0589753bb290bf680e2bd5668f6/8f77f/2023-error-5.png 346w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 346px) 100vw, 346px&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이제 다시 VScode로 돌아가서 스크립트를 실행하면 정상적으로 작동되는 것을 확인할 수 있다.
&lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 288px; &quot;&gt;
      &lt;a class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot; href=&quot;/static/1bc9eaf90e7179c3401877562162e1d1/477c9/2023-error-6.png&quot; style=&quot;display: block&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 17.72151898734177%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot; alt=&quot;result query&quot; title=&quot;result query&quot; src=&quot;/static/1bc9eaf90e7179c3401877562162e1d1/477c9/2023-error-6.png&quot; srcset=&quot;/static/1bc9eaf90e7179c3401877562162e1d1/c26ae/2023-error-6.png 158w,
/static/1bc9eaf90e7179c3401877562162e1d1/477c9/2023-error-6.png 288w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px&quot; style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;참고 자료&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.vmware.com/kr/vRealize-Automation/7.6/com.vmware.vra.iaas.blade.doc/GUID-C86DCF49-F23B-4B9C-9FD5-95524FB74F01.html&quot;&gt;https://docs.vmware.com/kr/vRealize-Automation/7.6/com.vmware.vra.iaas.blade.doc/GUID-C86DCF49-F23B-4B9C-9FD5-95524FB74F01.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://learn.microsoft.com/ko-kr/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_execution_policies?view=powershell-7.3&quot;&gt;https://learn.microsoft.com/ko-kr/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_execution_policies?view=powershell-7.3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[MySQL 언어 설정 에러(UTF-8)]]></title><description><![CDATA[문제 세션을 통한 로그인 기능을 구현 하던 중에 insert 쿼리 실행 시 아래와 같은 오류가 발생했다. 추론 컬럼에 맞지 않는 데이터라는데 webdbtbl_membermname 라는 걸 보니 해당 에러는 mname…]]></description><link>https://sirius506775.github.io/SQL/2023-sql-1/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://sirius506775.github.io/SQL/2023-sql-1/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 06 Jan 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h2&gt;문제&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;세션을 통한 로그인 기능을 구현 하던 중에 insert 쿼리 실행 시 아래와 같은 오류가 발생했다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;sql&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-sql&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sql&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;22007&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;1366&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;conn&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;76&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; Incorrect string &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;\xEC\x82\xAC\xEC\x9A\xA9...&apos;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;column&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token identifier&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;webdb&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token identifier&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;tbl_member&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token identifier&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;mname&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; at &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;row&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;추론&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;컬럼에 맞지 않는 데이터라는데 &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;for column &lt;/code&gt;webdb&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;.&lt;/code&gt;tbl_member&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;.&lt;/code&gt;mname&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt; at row 1&lt;/code&gt; 라는 걸 보니 해당 에러는 mname의 값이 문제가 되는 것 같다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;mname에 한글로 된 문자열이 들어간&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;sql&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-sql&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sql&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;insert&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;into&lt;/span&gt; tbl_member &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;mid&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; mpw&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; mname&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;values&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;user00&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;1111&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;사용자0&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;해결방법&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이 에러는 MySQL 언어 설정이 UTF-8이 되어 있지 않아서 생기는 문제이다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;sql&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-sql&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sql&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; tbl_member &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;CONVERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;TO&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;CHARSET&lt;/span&gt; utf8&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;쿼리 탭에 해당 테이블의 기본 설정을 UTF-8로 바꾸어주고 다시 쿼리를 날리면 정상적으로 데이터가 테이블에 insert 되는 것을 확인할 수 있다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 498px; &quot;&gt;
      &lt;a class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot; href=&quot;/static/c17051197346d8a709bc0e7402d4c8e5/79e1b/2023-sql-1.png&quot; style=&quot;display: block&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;
